{"tid":770513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★自\"煮\"硏發OS? ------「小霸王Z+」","createTime":"2018-08-07T07:01:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T09:27:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c37d244d81e3ab93ee332293af70fbd210027cca","tid":770513,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:01:45.000Z","msg":"電子產品公司小霸王早前在 China Joy 2018 活動中宣佈，推出全新遊戲主機「小霸王 Z+」，似是有意重返中國遊戲市場。<br />\n<br />\n在硬件方面，「小霸王 Z+」與超微半導體公司 AMD 合作，共同合作開發客製化的 Zen 架構 APU 處理器，對應 4 核心 8 線程設計，時脈 3GHz ，整合了 Vega 顯示架構。據稱整體運算效能可接近約 3.5 TFLOPS。廠方指「小霸王 Z+」的效能比 PlayStation 4 甚至 Xbox One 高，但不及 PlayStation 4 Pro 與 Xbox One X。<br />\n<br />\n「小霸王 Z+」搭載 8GB 記憶體﹑128GB SSD 與 1TB 硬碟容量。<span style=\"color: red;\">主機配有小霸王自家的作業系統外</span>，還搭載了正版 Windows 10，加上鍵盤和滑鼠，可當一般電腦使用。還可以下載 Steam 和 Microsoft Store 平台的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n「小霸王 Z+」的建議售價是人民幣 4998 元 ( 折合約港幣$ 5,735 元)，至於正式出售時間則有待官方確認。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/08/07/newgameconsolelaunchedbychinesefirm/wireless-home/desktop-pc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F08%2F07%2Fnewgameconsolelaunchedbychinesefirm%2Fwireless-home%2Fdesktop-pc%2F&d=Thze4iS1zEhPc8BOPh5Ksp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=14ed15c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/08/07/newgameconsolelaunchedbychinesefirm/wireless-home/desktop-pc/</a>"},{"pid":"7dd71bb5e4e9de5f3267d4174194411ef729aa74","tid":770513,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/photo-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Fphoto-1.jpg&h=3f3b2212&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bcc2697a44444aa8ce21102b30a39cdf9205ff8","tid":770513,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:04:32.000Z","msg":"中共木馬  不了"},{"pid":"b8f4b85b6bf9b5e2b6b92ab87e1f28105e645e77","tid":770513,